            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日跌逾1%  生科股逆市揚升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股顯著回吐，半日跌284點，科網股成跌市元兇，生科股造好，物流速遞股受捧，首掛維立志博(09887)飆1 倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數競價時段半日跌284點或1.11%，報25383，今早開跌135點0.53%，報25531點 ，早段最高見25585點，跌136點或0.53%，隨即跌幅擴大，最低見25363，挫304點或1.18%，為半日低位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌97點或1.69%，報5645點，今早開跌29點或0.51%，報5713點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數跌116點或1.26%，報9140點，今早開跌41點或0.45%，報9216點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌299點或1.16%，報25384，高水1點; 科指期貨半日跌98點或1.71%，報5643點，低水3點 ; 國指期貨半日跌9140點，跌128點或1.38%，低水5點。   </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1510.08億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科網股成跌市元兇，；阿里巴巴(09988)插2.16%，報117.7元；小米(01810)跌2.31%，報57.1元 ; 騰訊(00700)降1.62%，造548元；美團(03690)跌2.53%，報131元 ; 快手(01024)挫4.33%，造72.9元，為包尾藍籌；5股合計推低恒指186點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生科股炒上，藥明生物(02269)飆4.69%，造31.25元，為升幅最大藍籌；藥明康德(02359)升2.07%，報98.5元 ; 中國生物製藥(01177)升1.64%，報6.82元。中國抗體(03681)勁升19.39%，造3.14元；荃信生物(02509)升6.38%，造19.68元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">康龍化成(03759)急升8.43%，造22.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雲頂新耀(01952) 折讓約10.12%配股，半日跌8.96%，報70.6元 ; 科濟藥業(02171)預告虧損減逾77%，股價升轉跌，半日跌4.29%，報23.65元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">物流速遞股跑出，順豐(06936)漲2.89%，造46.3元；中通快遞(02057)升2.4%，造162元；極兔速遞(01519)升3.46%，造10.18元；京東物流(02618)升2.57%；KLN(00636)則升2.75%，造8.96元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">OSL(00863)折讓15.34%配股，半日挫6.59%，報16.44元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首掛維立志博(09887)飆99%，報69.65元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120964-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be1-%e7%94%9f%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-25 12:40:24",
